{"tid":208538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠勸張子強從良 圖劫獄救葉繼歡","createTime":"2017-04-19T15:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T15:42:50.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85a4a756444071cacca99a6b6287df67c343e2f5","tid":208538,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170419/501810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170419%2F501810&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=f50c5df3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170419%2F501810&h=564e84d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170419/501810</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一代賊王，「大富翁」張子強，最後在內地伏法，終年四十三歲。在他短短廿七年的犯罪生涯，犯下大案無數，同他交手的全部都不是泛泛之輩。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠和張子強的相遇，絕對是世紀交手。一個是極惡凶徒，一個是亞洲首富。當大仔李澤鉅被綁架，張子強單人匹馬綁住炸彈上門，絕對有膽識。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠在13年11月接受南方報刊訪問，他就大爆兩人對話，原來李嘉誠曾經多次叫他做個好人：「你拿那麼多錢，下半世夠用了，現在遠走高飛，洗心革面。」<br />\n<br />\n之後張子強亦找他，聲稱他輸錢，問李嘉誠點樣投資，李嘉誠只係講：遠走高飛，否則下場可悲。張子強亦應驗這句說話。他為人好賭，又喜歡豪使，曾經試過兩晚輸了六千萬，所以要繼續犯案，走入末路。<br />\n<br />\n雖然他對敵人不手軟，但是對自己手足，絕對講足義氣，義氣對象，就是另一位賊王，葉繼歡。葉繼歡和張子強在獄中相識，及後合謀綁架李澤鉅。但之後葉繼歡由大陸坐艇由西環上岸，被軍裝警用槍打傷，自此半身不遂，在赤柱監獄坐三十年監。<br />\n<br />\n當 時張子強一心要炸赤柱監獄，在馬草壟一間石屋儲存近800公斤炸藥，不過被警方搗破，他亦被逼潛逃內地。而炸監獄的傳聞，亦在張子強另一位拜結兄弟得到印 證，他就是有赤柱監獄揸fit人的「搞事雄」劉國雄。劫獄不成，張子強亦被逼北上，眾多的前因後果，令到一代賊王，最終步入滅亡之路。"},{"pid":"dcfbadd697c044d210bc470fccd4e99613f50881","tid":208538,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"乜撚標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337f2057085ee185412319a1ef7285435944bd38","tid":208538,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇內容以為誠仔劫獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3de69c94762953982ff4a6fdabecd97fc6f5768","tid":208538,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇內容以為誠仔劫獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08540d2ddf3fdec7e375f03951bb8d5bcda89c0","tid":208538,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2d0fb14829661f96ec3e3066aa36a57c27f631","tid":208538,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇內容以為誠仔劫獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實<br />\n唔睇內容都估到誠仔唔會劫獄<br />\n<br />\n雖然標題真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}